class ZCL_MFP_LOCK_UTILITIES definition
  public
  final
  create private .

public section.

*"* public components of class ZCL_MFP_LOCK_UTILITIES
*"* do not include other source files here!!!
  class-methods LOCK_OBJECTS
    importing
      !IV_EBELN type EBELN
    exporting
      !SUBRC type SY-SUBRC
    changing
      !MESSAGES type BAPIRET2_T .
  class-methods UNLOCK_OBJECT
    importing
      !IV_EBELN type EBELN .
  PROTECTED SECTION.
*"* protected components of class ZCL_MFP_LOCK_UTILITIES
